":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T09:23:36.000Z","msg":"幾好,good try <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T11:08:07.000Z","msg":"希望樓主你個答案係高質過呢個<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdf778c6a3c7d9e91f58f28c2c5109d57d600368","tid":2230504,"uid":262886,"like":4,"dislike":29,"score":-25,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T12:07:11.000Z","msg":"答案係貂蟬<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W17wv7X.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW17wv7X.jpg&h=4dfbc963&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N2T7OUF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN2T7OUF.jpg&h=3e13e25f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n相傳貂蟬係王允利用美人計離間董卓同呂布兩人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />王允先將貂蟬獻比董卓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n董卓自納貂蟬後， 情色所凝， 月餘不理政事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sCYLAzQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsCYLAzQ.jpg&h=330ee21b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n而呂布亦同貂蟬另有姦情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L4jVXOX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL4jVXOX.jpg&h=867724aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n貂蟬為咗勾引呂布，暪住董卓同呂布偷情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n為咗令呂布沉船，着迷於佢，貂蟬自然會使用佢畢生絕世口技<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2WV6j1T.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2WV6j1T.jpg&h=5685c64f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n試想像吓，含住呂布碌撚嘅貂蟬<br />\n「唔....啊啊...唔唔....好大啊～」<br />\n「奉先...啊～好大啊...好味啊...唔唔」<br />\n肯定會幫呂布奶到雪雪聲，食到津津有味<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dllm.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dllm.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dllm.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2PkRv8P.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2PkRv8P.jpg&h=5406cb80&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n而呂布（奉先）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tFdjE2v.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtFdjE2v.jpg&h=3051e39c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t5hXrHy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft5hXrHy.jpg&h=74e18e2c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n所以答案就係貂蟬<br />\n因為佢好鐘意成日偷食奉先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AdBJnfZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAdBJnfZ.jpg&h=8b4c5970&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n需要具備豐富歷史知識同邏輯思考，先可以解答到依條難題<br />\nEASY，多謝各位<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d136c4534f0267b1af405452d5468e0c98b434a1","tid":2230504,"uid":76080,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bdf778c6a3c7d9e91f58f28c2c5109d57d600368","tid":2230504,"uid":262886,"like":4,"dislike":29,"score":-25,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T12:07:11.000Z","msg":"答案係貂蟬<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W17wv7X.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW17wv7X.jpg&h=4dfbc963&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N2T7OUF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN2T7OUF.jpg&h=3e13e25f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n相傳貂蟬係王允利用美人計離間董卓同呂布兩人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bou